    "description": [
      "An old wagon lies buried in the mud near the shore of a murky bog, dark green lichen already finding a home upon its timbers.  A light green carpet of minute plant life floats on the surface of the stagnant water, an occasional bubble parting the greenery as it expands outwards toward the shore.  At the edge of the marsh, stands of cattails mark the entrance to a shadowed archway beneath the burdened boughs of an ancient willow tree."
